  "interop_compat_risks": null,
  "all_platforms": true,
  "all_platforms_descr": "It is supported on all platforms because it is purely a browser-internal optimization that changes when existing OS clipboard APIs are called (deferring from read() time to getType() time), without requiring any new platform-specific clipboard capabilities or OS-level API changes.\n ",
